@startuml
title Manage Users Activity Diagram
|Admin|
start
:View Users List;
|System|
:Display User List;
|Admin|
:Click "Add User";
|System|
:Display Add Form;
|Admin|
:Fill User Details (Name, Email, Role);
:Submit Form;
